{"tid":1602801,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆我個街，竟然冇留意到雪櫃貼咗張狗署磁石","createTime":"2019-09-29T13:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T14:52:26.000Z","uid":209873,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"31c171a747ffbb9de7c4f3899518fbac60466dae","tid":1602801,"uid":209873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日行完行街街，返到屋企好口渴，諗住拎杯凍飲時，突然發現我個雪櫃上面貼咗呢張磁石<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdO9xE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdO9xE4.jpg&h=ed15c4ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為呢舊野我估都有十幾年歷史，所以我同屋企人已經完全習慣咗佢嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同老豆講完，佢即刻嬲撚到叫我即刻掉咗佢，好撚眼冤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就諗，其實後面塊磁石係無辜架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />於是我將前面張紙撕走，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EBZUTH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EBZUTH.jpg&h=ee19dfee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後貼番張最近先收到嘅靚靚關公叔叔貼紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vF5zJNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvF5zJNC.jpg&h=f2a6c3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsize幾乎完美fit曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成舊雪櫃即刻充滿住正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBSuxF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBSuxF3.jpg&h=1e796355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n、繅<br />\n因為大西北撚路途太遙遠，怕畀狗咬所以冇特登收集文宣，所以暫時得咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2bc4e654ba0b0eb79575571ba74be52b448292e","tid":1602801,"uid":104811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"聽日 930 全港三罷"},{"pid":"c07579c2fe7d00ada9a71c8af050646238653e3b","tid":1602801,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c6c118509bec6642d1c1197eff1e3879b01ec3c","tid":1602801,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"721 無個打得通"}]}